@SmartOrders.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5101

### ① Index the order catalog (run once after Qdrant is up)
POST {{SmartOrders.Api_HostAddress}}/api/catalog/index
Accept: application/json

###

### ② STEP 1 — Process clinical text
### Returns AwaitingConfirmation=true + SubmissionAgentResponse (the agent's "please confirm" message)
### Copy the "validatedOrdersJson" field from the response to use in Step 2.
POST {{SmartOrders.Api_HostAddress}}/api/orders/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clinicalText": "Order a CBC and chest X-ray for anemia workup. Patient has type 2 diabetes."
}

###

### ③ STEP 2 — Provider confirms and submits
### Paste the validatedOrdersJson from Step 1 response.
### providerConfirmation options: "submit all", "submit CBC only", "cancel"
POST {{SmartOrders.Api_HostAddress}}/api/orders/submit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "validatedOrdersJson": "<paste validatedOrdersJson from /process response>",
  "providerConfirmation": "submit all"
}

###
